                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JAMES GROVE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Supposing him to receive money on the 31st of August, when ought he to have given it to you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> On the same day—when he came home that evening, I asked if Mr. Church had paid him; he said no, he sent his compliments, and he would call in a day or two—there was then another barrel of ale ordered by another drayman, and I found this out on the 7th of September.</p>
